How to see all the commits info in a short format
# git log --oneline
How to find commits done by a particular user in a Project 
# git log --author=<name or email>
How to unstage a file
# git reset HEAD <filename>
git revert command 
# git revert <CID>
git revert helps to undo a commit > git revert should be applied after u done the commit on a file.
** applicable on the committed files.
How to undo changes before commit?
# git checkout -- filename




